Package it.polimi.ingsw.network.common.deliverable

Class Assets

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.network.common.deliverable.Deliverable
      • it.polimi.ingsw.network.common.deliverable.Assets
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Assets
extends Deliverable
    Assets-type Deliverables are used to display with colour the Game status. They're always sent by the Server and received by the Client. The server does not require (or indeed expect) a Response after sending one. Not to be confused with Info, which is used to convey simple information to the user.
    See Also:
